      "content": "I'm a project manager at a construction firm. We've hit a significant delay on the bridge project due to some supply chain mismanagement on our end, but the client is extremely deadline-driven. If I tell them the delay is due to 'unforeseen geological complexities' in the riverbed, what's the most professional way to document that in the weekly progress report to ensure we don't face penalties?"
